                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Store at 25°C (77°F); excursion permitted to 15°C - 30°C (59° - 86°F).</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>Protect from freezing. [See USP Controlled Room Temperature.] Flammable. Keep away from heat and open flame.</paragraph>
